The original code has been modified, in particular:
  - re-focused on a lean, protocol-first core (CallResource + CheckHealth);
  - Apache Arrow / dataframe (QueryData) and Grafana Live streaming support
    moved behind opt-in cargo features (`data`, `stream`);
  - renamed crates to `grafana-plugin-sdk-rs` / `grafana-plugin-sdk-rs-macros`.

